#. type: Plain text
#: pcbnew_routing.adoc:227
msgid ""
"As you move the mouse, a track is drawn connecting the origin of the track "
"with the current mouse position. The track will be drawn with at most two "
"segments (for example, rightwards, then a switch to diagonally). Clicking "
"while routing locks in the corner node."
msgstr ""
"Come si muove il mouse, viene creata una pista che connette l'origine della "
"pista con la posizione corrente del mouse. La pista verrà disegnata con "
